Telegram message arrives
        ↓
Telethon detects it
        ↓
handler(event) is called
        ↓
Check chat_id (security)
        ↓
Is it voice?
   ├── YES → download → STT → text
   └── NO  → use raw text
        ↓
Check is_command()
   ├── YES → handle_command()
   │         ↓
   │     returns result
   │         ↓
   │     send file / message
   │
   └── NO → ask_ai()
             ↓
         send reply